---
import SectionPageLayout from "../layouts/SectionPageLayout.astro";
---

<SectionPageLayout
  title="Accessibility | Sakai LMS"
  description="The Sakai community is committed to making core Sakai features accessible and usable by the greatest number of users."
  kicker="Accessibility"
  heading="Accessibility"
>
  <article class="hard-border block-shadow-soft bg-[var(--sakai-paper)] p-6">
    <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-[var(--sakai-ink)]">
      The Sakai community is committed to ensuring all core features are accessible and usable by the greatest number of users, including people with disabilities.
    </p>
    <p class="mt-4 text-sm leading-relaxed text-[var(--sakai-ink-soft)]">
      Sakai is developed to meet or exceed recognized international accessibility standards, including WCAG 2.2 Level A and AA success criteria,
      and uses emerging practices like WAI-ARIA to support adaptive technologies.
    </p>
    <p class="mt-4 text-sm leading-relaxed text-[var(--sakai-ink-soft)]">
      The community regularly evaluates accessibility and publishes results for transparency and continuous improvement.
    </p>
  </article>

  <section class="grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-3">
    <a href="https://confluence.sakaiproject.org/display/2ACC/Accessibility+Working+Group" class="hard-border block-shadow-soft bg-white p-5">
      <h2 class="sans text-lg font-black uppercase text-[var(--sakai-ink)]">Accessibility Working Group</h2>
      <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-[var(--sakai-ink-soft)]">Join discussions and ongoing accessibility efforts.</p>
    </a>
    <a href="https://www.sakailms.org/accessibility/accessibility-strategy" class="hard-border block-shadow-soft bg-white p-5">
      <h2 class="sans text-lg font-black uppercase text-[var(--sakai-ink)]">Accessibility Strategy</h2>
      <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-[var(--sakai-ink-soft)]">Review Sakai's strategy and design goals.</p>
    </a>
    <a href="https://www.sakailms.org/accessibility/vpat" class="hard-border block-shadow-soft bg-white p-5">
      <h2 class="sans text-lg font-black uppercase text-[var(--sakai-ink)]">Sakai VPAT</h2>
      <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-[var(--sakai-ink-soft)]">Access current VPAT information for Sakai.</p>
    </a>
  </section>
</SectionPageLayout>
